**AI-powered navigation system that optimizes routes for air quality, traffic, and health impact**

<img src="assets/ecoroute-demo.gif" width="800" alt="EcoRoute Demo">

## ‚ú® Features

- **Pollution-Aware Routing**: Avoids high PM2.5/PM10 zones
- **Smart Traffic Prediction**: Random Forest model outperforms Google Maps ETAs
- **Health Alerts**: Real-time air quality warnings
- **AI Assistant**: Llama 3.2 chatbot explains route choices
- **Public Transport Suggestions**: Recommends cleaner alternatives

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

| Component               | Technology |
|-------------------------|------------|
| Frontend                | HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Google Maps API |
| Backend                 | Python, Flask |
| Machine Learning        | Scikit-learn (Random Forest) |
| AI Chatbot              | Llama 3.2 via Ollama |
| Database                | SQLite |
| Deployment              | Docker, Render (or your hosting) |

